"This doesn't look like a valid field key from the wp_usermeta database "
"table.\n"
"\n"
"If you're not sure what your field keys are please check your database.\n"
"\n"
"Registering invalid keys for sync may result in unexpected behavior. Most "
"likely it just won't do anything."
msgstr ""
"这看起来不是 wp_usermeta 数据库表中的有效字段键。\n"
"\n"
